    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 18th level, you can spend 6 @Compendium[5e-complete-fr.5e-class-features.7hAcETWHOVguR2ZF]{Sorcery Points} as a bonus action to transform yourself into a shadowy form. In this form, you have resistance to all damage except <strong>force </strong>and <strong>radiant damage</strong>, and you can move through other creatures and objects as if they were difficult terrain. You take 5 force damage if you end your turn inside an object.</p>\n<p>You remain in this form for 1 minute. It ends early if you are <strong>incapacitated</strong>, if you <strong>die</strong>, or if you dismiss it as a bonus action.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: After adding this feature to your character, set Resource Consumption to Item Uses: Font of Magic: 6</em></p>\n</section>",
